  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this observational study is to find characteristics and risk stratification
      methods for identification of subjects who have increased risk of death, especially sudden
      cardiac death, after acute myocardial infarction.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
